out of two years prior,

395
00:22:24,760 --> 00:22:28,620
so, you know, I guess they weren't that
smart, to figure out where to protest.

396
00:22:30,240 --> 00:22:33,050
But I remember listening to
stuff on the Internet.

397
00:22:33,520 --> 00:22:37,590
I would listen to some of their ideas
that they would talk about,

398
00:22:38,240 --> 00:22:40,240
because fan support
is very important,

399
00:22:40,600 --> 00:22:44,850
and I wanted them to be
happy with Transformers.

400
00:22:45,520 --> 00:22:47,480
But I was trying to introduce
a world of people

