403
00:22:57,480 --> 00:23:00,320
because I was able to make
this movie more accessible

404
00:23:00,800 --> 00:23:03,399
to the non-fan, I guess.

405
00:23:03,840 --> 00:23:07,949
So I must say right now,
lam a true Transformer fan.

406
00:23:08,600 --> 00:23:10,740
l have probably thought
about robots

407
00:23:11,120 --> 00:23:13,050
