almost Pentagon-type quality encryption.

416
00:23:46,720 --> 00:23:50,410
And they actually personally hacked
into my personal computer.

417
00:23:51,000 --> 00:23:54,440
And they were able to steal
one script.

418
00:23:55,000 --> 00:23:58,790
