l was able to get the script back.

419
00:23:59,400 --> 00:24:01,430
But luckily it only
got out once.

420
00:24:01,800 --> 00:24:06,120
So there were so many leaks that I
decided to actually keep the script...

421
00:24:08,560 --> 00:24:12,210
